body_html:
@DaveyTao we encountered a PermissionDeniedError in #4913 where TensorFlow was being configured to save stuff in /tmp rather than creating a special subdirectory. It's possible this could be related to that.

Aside from that, I'm going to close this issue, because there isn't enough information here for closer examination or reproduction. I'll reopen this issue if provided new information.
